INSTALL_MSG: TempVoice - Creates Tempary voice channels for people in public discord servers - Creates a file of the channels that have been made - Usage: [p]voice [name of channel]
NAME: TempVoice
SHORT: Creates voice channels that will be deleted once empty
DESCRIPTION: This cog - TempVoice will create Voice channels that will later be deleted after a set interval - optional argument of the name of the channel - Usage: [p]voice [name of channel]
